                </div>
                <hr class="my-3" />

                <div class="w-full grow grid flex-row grid-cols-2 gap-5">
                    <HomeScreenNav title="Programmer" Icon={CodeXmlIcon} path="/programming">
                        While only really beginning 4 years ago, I've really been coding my whole life.
                    </HomeScreenNav>

                    <HomeScreenNav title="Musician" Icon={MusicIcon} path="/music">
                        I've been making music my whole life, both in music production software
                        and with actual instruments.
                    </HomeScreenNav>

                    <HomeScreenNav title="Athlete" Icon={SportShoeIcon} path="/athletics">
                        I've been competing in track and field for 4 years, as a high jumper and
                        pole vaulter.
                    </HomeScreenNav>

                    <HomeScreenNav title="And more!" Icon={PlusIcon} path="/misc">
                        Of course, I can't fit all of my hobbies into three buckets.
                        Here are some misc. projects.
                    </HomeScreenNav>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</MainLayout>

